OL,4,CWingate fire: Ex-marine's home
OL,5,Cdestroyed 'after standing up to yobs'
OL,6, A teacher and ex-Royal Marine said his
OL,7, family is lucky to be alive after a
OL,8, suspected arson attack which destroyed
OL,9, their home in County Durham.
OL,11,FSean Ivey, from Wingate, fled to safety
OL,12,Fwith his wife and two children after a
OL,13,Ffire broke out early on Thursday.
OL,15,FMr Ivey, who served in Afghanistan and
OL,16,FIraq, believed he was targeted after
OL,17,Fstanding up to anti-social behaviour.
OL,19,FTwo men have been arrested and Durham
OL,20,FPolice issued a 48-hour dispersal order
OL,21,Fin the area.
